sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Worker
    participant C as XR/Mobile Client
    participant E as Edge Inference Gateway
    participant P as Procedure Engine
    participant A as Audit/Evidence Service
    participant D as Dashboard

    W->>C: Start inspection session
    C->>P: Load SOP version and first step
    P-->>C: Step conditions and thresholds
    loop every sampled frame / evidence capture
        C->>E: Send frame/snapshot
        E-->>C: Detection results
        C->>P: Submit observations
        P-->>C: Step state: pass/fail/uncertain
        alt fail
            C-->>W: XR warning and correction guide
        else uncertain
            C-->>W: Retake or request supervisor approval
        else pass
            C-->>W: Advance to next step
        end
        P->>A: Write audit event
        C->>A: Upload evidence snapshot
        A-->>D: Update dashboard metrics
    end
